    <note>Li(2) Zhichun [1000] Posthumously purged as Yuanyou coalition member. Zhiyi's [3484] brother. Recommended by Wen(2) Yanbo [1953]. Zhichun and Zhiyi have the same generational name as Zhiji [1001]. Their sisters' husbands were He(2) Zhongli's [678] son, He(2) Jingchu [3385], and Lin(1) Shao [1166]. Hejian FZ (1540), 26.9a lists Zhichun as a Cangzhou, Wudi Xian person. CHECK sources for possible information on lineage migration. Jiangxi TZ, 9.31a; XCB, 266.2a, 269.23a-23b, 278.14a, 300.13a, 330.12a, 350.11a, 382.17a, 396.1a, 382.17a, 394.17a, 429.14b, 443.1a, 453.2b; XCBSB, 10.2a; Shen Shi san, 39.71b. CBD, 2, 946-7.</note>
